  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: when login for the first time after upgrading to the new build, \"Send\" button will be disabled until relogin to the app.\r\nCould reproduce 2 times from 5 attempts.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nCan send message\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nSend button is disabled\r\n<img width=\"346\" alt=\"12345\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/48122820-c55d9e80-e278-11e8-919e-078fb39aa18c.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n**Prerequisites**: user already have account on one of the previous nightly\r\n\r\n**Scenario 1:**\r\n- Install (replace) last nightly\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Log in\r\n- Try to send a message\r\n\r\n**Scenario 2:**\r\n- Install last nightly\r\n- Create new account\r\n- Join to public chat\r\n- Try to send a message\r\n\r\nSometimes relogin can help, but not always.\r\nMy assumption that application for some reason lost connection with mailserver and no warning is shown, because in all cases messages are not fetching.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: nightly 07/11/2018\r\n* Operating System: Mac OSx\r\n* Video: https://monosnap.com/file/CNkcaLYFPYQUSBeu14xQ1MXhsGMIb4\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\n* StatusIm.log: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1i3MQHreDdJ5Ah2yZm2gxsJRY0JFBbcoq\r\n\r\n\r\n",
